# Defaults from the Inputs table: count=1, skip=0, hz=1.0. A single trigger
# yields exactly one pulse (the "convert a gate into a short trigger" use case).
# At tickrate 8, hz default 1 -> period 8 -> pulse is 4 ticks high then done.
tickrate 8
patch <<<
[burst]
    trigger = I1
    output  = O1
>>>
@0 expect O1 0
@1 set I1 1
@1 expect O1 1
@2 set I1 0
@2 expect O1 1
@3 expect O1 1
@4 expect O1 1
@5 expect O1 0
@6 expect O1 0
@8 expect O1 0
@12 expect O1 0
